<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        strong {
            color: #e44d26;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>OTP Verification</h2>
        <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) is: <strong><%= token %></strong></p>
        <p>Please use this OTP to complete the verification process.</p>
        <p>This OTP is valid for a short period of time.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Thank you!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
